OL,6,FProtests have erupted at schools across
OL,7,Fthe country after pupils were banned
OL,8,Ffrom using the toilet during lessons.
OL,10,FHundreds of students demonstrated in
OL,11,Fschools in Cornwall, Yorkshire and
OL,12,FLincolnshire. It is claimed that in one
OL,13,Fprotest at Penrice Academy, St Austell,
OL,14,FCornwall pupils broke fences and
OL,15,Fflipped tables when the new rules were
OL,16,Fannounced.
OL,18,FRules introduced at Penrice Academy say
OL,19,Fthat pupils, including those who are
OL,20,Fmenstruating, must ask for a red card
OL,21,Fwhen they need to use the toilet.
OL,3,CStudents stage protests across the UK
OL,4,Cover toilet 'prison rules'
